snippet.title: Torchlight: Infinite - Official Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Set 200 years after Torchlight 2, Torchlight Infinite is an action-RPG that features four heroes and a couple dozen skill trees to customize your character's playstyle with. Pre-register on the official website (torchlight.xd.com) to be eligible to participate in the closed beta that's starting soon.

#IGN #Gaming
